---
title: Smokey Beef Strips & Garlic Rice with Aioli & Walnut Slaw
description: There’s a hint of smokiness in the air and it’s coming from these beef strips, the All-American mild spice does wonders
when cooked into beef and served on top of a bed of rice. Not to mention, the smokey aioli tossed through the
slaw. It’s a firestorm of flavour tonight!
